    <p>Let's illustrate these ideas with a more complicated example that combines all of the features we have discussed so far. </p> 
    <p>
      This upcoming example will also utilize vertical asymptotes from <xref ref="ssec-locating-va">Locating Vertical Asymptotes</xref> 
      as well as horizontal asymptotes from <xref ref="dominant-terms">Calculating Horizontal Asymptotes</xref> back in Chapter 1.
    </p>


